The paper proposes a novel approach for eye movement detection using convolutional neural networks (CNN), which is a popular technique in computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves signal processing and neuroscience, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper involves automated detection and classification, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
